# рџ”ђ AuthSystem вЂ” Secure Script Authentication

Full-stack key authentication system:  
**Node.js backend** В· **Owner web dashboard** В· **Discord bot** В· **Roblox in-game panel**

---

## Architecture

```
auth-system/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ backend/          Node.js + Express API (SQLite)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ server.js
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ db.js         Schema + query helpers
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ crypto.js     AES-256-CBC encrypt/decrypt + script wrapper
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ middleware/
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ ownerAuth.js   JWT guard
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ routes/
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ auth.js        Owner login
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ whitelist.js   User CRUD
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ hwid.js        HWID reset
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ script.js      Upload + secure delivery
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ frontend/         Owner dashboard (served by Express)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.html    Landing page
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ login.html    Owner login
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ dashboard.html  Full panel (users В· scripts В· logs)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ panel.lua     Served at /panel.lua for Roblox to HttpGet
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ css/global.css
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ bot/
